				<div class="col-lg-6  text-justify">
				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">MIZORAM</h1>
				<p>Mizoram is a mountainous state resting in the southernmost tip of the north-eastern region of India.  A land of great natural beauty having rich flora and fauna it generally has a pleasant climate throughout the year. The scenic landscapes of bluish hills and mountains , steep rocky cliffs , serene lakes and deep valleys of gurgling rivers with its spectacular waterfalls makes the state an ideal destination for natural lovers.</p><p>
				The fantastic array of wildlife especially the bird is an added attraction. To the more adventure spirit, the rugged terrains and swift flowing rivers are the ideal for various outdoor sports and adventure activities.
				</p>
